title: TYPE O NEGATiVE (Ultimate Fan Pack.1991-2007).[V2]
description:
TYPE O NEGATiVE [Ultimate Fan Pack.Video/Discography 1991-2007].[V2]

One of my all-time favourite bands.
All audio files ripped directly from the original CDs from my personal collection.

Ripped @LameInsaneQuality (MP3.320kb/s.48kHz):

Type O Negative [1991] Slow, Deep And Hard
Type O Negative [1992] The Origin Of The Feces (Not Live At Brighton Beach)
Type O Negative [1993] Bloody Kisses
Type O Negative [1996] October Rust
Type O Negative [1998] After Dark [Video Album]
Type O Negative [1999] World Coming Down
Type O Negative [2000] The Least Worst Of [Unedited Version]
Type O Negative [2003] Life Is Killing Me
Type O Negative [2006] Symphony For The Devil [Live][Video Album]
Type O Negative [2006] The Best Of Type O Negative [Roadrunner Records]
Type O Negative [2007] Dead Again [Red Edition]

NOTE: The 'Life Is Killing Me' CD is the Special Edition, with a Bonus CD containing 7 previously unreleased tracks. But I chose to put that Bonus CD together with the 'The Least Worst Of Type O Negative' folder, for those tracks were outtakes from that album.

[All files tagged with info, links and CD cover.]

It also includes de Video-Albums (*.avi): 'After Dark' [1998], 'Symphony For The Devil' [2006] and the Bonus DVD included in the 'Dead Again [Red Edition]' Digipack.
